channel.title: Willing to help a noob for a level 94 no joke.come here if you succed
channel.description:
Hello I am Mod Only.Not a real mod just a name.i played runescape for about 5 years.havent played over 3 years.i found out that wild was out mate..and i got really upset so here is my deal.i found out about this client called RS503HD it's a 503 client but it has a Anti-Leech that everytime i run it it won't let me run it i know its from noobs so they dont go and leech a 100% work mate.but my point is this.. here is a pic.http://img381.imageshack.us/img381/9783/nooxat8.png thats the picture of the run and it shows problems on it. now heres the second pic.http://img381.imageshack.us/img381/5601/fffffo8.png
i need to know what to delete and what to add if you dont wanna tell me thats fine mate.the username of the runescape account is darkrider20 has 28 days of member left.. worth it aint it? if you think all of this is a joke or b.s just add me in rs.and trust me mate you wont regret it.don't be greedy like the java nerds who think just because they know all about java coding doesnt mean everybody has to do it for it,so they can know as well.. mate.thats why there is the word called "HELP"..if someone doesnt know nothing about java then why not just givw them a hand.huh? i mean.. the account is worth it.ha lots of good pking loots. from wild.well pm reply to this post if your good enough willing to help.if not then very well then.. thanks.
